{"tid":2242169,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"深入淺出–牛究竟天生有沒有角？","createTime":"2020-10-13T21:59:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-14T04:55:23.000Z","uid":38861,"like":52,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"518ee4b751aa7f62d24b3c4ee55f399110e81342","tid":2242169,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T21:59:21.000Z","msg":"動物的品種不同，其特徵亦會有所不同。以狗為例的話，金毛尋羊犬以及臘腸狗就是非常鮮明的例證。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4fDkfmK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4fDkfmK.jpg&h=0c602b78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n至於牛隻，農場飼養用的大致分為兩種，主力出產牛奶的乳牛(Daily Cattle)和主力屠宰成肉類出售的肉用牛(Beef Cattle)。<br />\n<br />\n各舉一例的話，前者品種例子為Holstein(荷斯坦)，而後者則為較為廣泛認識的Angus(安格斯)。<br />\n<br />\n牛天生會否長角，將視乎品種而定。大多數的乳牛品種天生均長有角，而食用牛多數的品種則天生無角。<br />\n<br />\n這裡讓農夫感到煩惱的是，乳牛隻會利用頭上的角互相攻擊對方甚至自己。<br />\n因此慣常的做法會麻醉牛隻然後再進行除角手術，以免牛隻受傷因而損失獲利，但這做法引起動物權益成員的關注及爭議，認為此舉會對牛隻帶來創傷。<br />\n<br />\n（圖2）最為有效率及一勞永逸的解決辦法，自當然就是培育沒有長角的品種，一直傳遞下去。<br />\n有科學家致力尋求發現，發現牛隻基因染色體1的某一段位置的重覆區域，將會導致乳牛品種不會長出牛角。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4UBh11S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4UBh11S.jpg&h=a0fc6cb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（圖3）因此，他們嘗試抽取長角品種的皮膚細胞，利用CRISPR基因編輯技術在那段基因區域上加添重覆區域（Ref1)，再經過一系列的工序，將已編輯的細胞人工培植到牛隻身上，觀察誕下的胎兒會否長出牛角。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oU6Rm1U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoU6Rm1U.jpg&h=40015a97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（圖4）最終所誕下的牛隻的而且確沒有長角，但因器官衰竭等問題很快便與世長辭。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NsVntHA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNsVntHA.png&h=0b040aa1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n這研究確實了CRISPR技術在牛隻的應用，但顯然仍有一系列的應用問題需要改善。在這實驗中，6隻人工培植受孕的牛隻中，只有一隻成功誕下嬰兒。<br />\n<br />\n至於為何不重點培育沒有長角品種的乳牛，原因是牠的產奶量較其他有角品種的最少。<br />\n<br />\n農父及科學家的最終目標，當然就是希望培植沒有長角而產奶量豐盛的牛隻。但這做法是否符合動物權益，這又會是一場永無休止的辯論。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去<span class=\"blue\">Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單</span>俾一個<span class=\"green\">like</span>以及<span class=\"red\">Bookmark</span>，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=Tp8cMPEgSVVC2rtXaxUH2pS9c5E4FlifGpQIAZCXP1E%3D&h=c4af209e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「<span class=\"gold\">買一嚿/半嚿薯仔</span>」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=Tp8cMPEgSVVC2rtXaxUH2pS9c5E4FlifGpQIAZCXP1E%3D&h=80ab61e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有興趣接收科學資訊的話，歡迎follow IG: potatopigtongue。<br />\n<br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://www.nature.com/articles/s41598-020-70531-y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nature.com%2Farticles%2Fs41598-020-70531-y&d=Tp8cMPEgSVVC2rtXaxUH2pS9c5E4FlifGpQIAZCXP1E%3D&h=c7f6b638\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nature.com/articles/s41598-020-70531-y</a>"},{"pid":"d73ea4b92aec01c967c305efb5ec89df8ca6fd6a","tid":2242169,"uid":38861,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T22:00:26.000Z","msg":"Dairy Cattle<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e51ddc8513dc20e2c6034aabbb65cf7fa695433e","tid":2242169,"uid":131522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB